# my-new-package

go to [mnp](https://www.npmjs.com/package/mnp) for the cli.

`my-new-package` is a new Node.js npm package.

## `myNewPackage():void`

Call this function to get a result you want.

```js
const myNewPackage = require('my-new-package')

myNewPackage()
```
